These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-1::.
House: ranch-style, art-deco
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: april, january
2 different games are played: monopoly, whist
2 different pets are kept: mouse, cat
1. the owner of the cat is on the left or right of the person playing whist##3
2. the art-deco house is in an even position##4
3. the person who's birthday is in january is the ranch-style house##1
4. the owner of the cat is on the right of the owner of the mouse##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |
| House      | ranch-style  | art-deco   |
| Birthday   | january     | april   |
| Game         | whist | monopoly |
| Pet     | mouse | cat    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-2::.
The people have 2 different jobs:  mechanic, bartender
House: craftsman, futuristic
The people have 2 different hobbies: baking, fishing
2 different games are played: scrabble, chess
1. the person who's hobby is fishing is in an odd position##4
2. the craftsman house is the person playing chess##1
3. the bartender is on the right of the futuristic house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |
| Job          | mechanic     | bartender |
| House   | futuristic | craftsman  |
| Hobby           | fishing         | baking     |
| Game     | scrabble   | chess    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-3::.
2 different games are played: scrabble, whist
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: d&b, rock
There are 2 different favourite colors: blue, red
There 2 different types of food: peas, cabbage
1. the person eating cabbage is on the left or right of the fan of rock##3
2. the person who likes red is on the right of the fan of rock##1
3. the person playing scrabble is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |       2       |
| Game    | whist     | scrabble |
| Music-Genre         | rock | d&b    |
| Color         | blue         | red        |
| Food   | peas         | cabbage    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-4::.
2 different pets are kept: fish, ferret
City: san-francisco, miami
2 different games are played: bridge, chess
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: mystery, superhero
1. the person playing chess is on the right of the person playing bridge##1
2. the person traveling to miami is on the left of the owner of the fish##1
3. the person watching superhero movies is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |
| Pet      | ferret     | fish |
| City          | miami   | san-francisco  |
| Game         | bridge | chess     |
| Movie-Genre   | mystery  | superhero         |

