.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-5::.
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: climbing, badminton
There are 2 different nationalities: german, pakistani
There 2 different types of food: banana, pomegranate
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: march, august
1. the person eating banana is on the right of the person who's sport is climbing##1
2. the person who's birthday is in august is in an odd position##4
3. the pakistani is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2      |
| Sport      | climbing | badminton       |
| Nationality           | pakistani      | german     |
| Food   | pomegranate       | banana   |
| Birthday           | august          | march |

