.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-6::.
There 2 different types of food: asparagus, eggplant
2 different games are played: scrabble, poker
The people use 2 different means of transport: tram, taxi
House: ranch-style, gothic-revival
1. the gothic-revival house is in an even position##4
2. the person playing poker is on the far left or far right##3
3. the person eating eggplant is the person playing scrabble##1
4. the person driving the tram is on the left of the person playing poker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2     |
| Food           | eggplant | asparagus    |
| Game   | scrabble       | poker |
| Transport           | tram         | taxi    |
| House         | ranch-style    | gothic-revival   |

