The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: tulip, daisy
1. the person who growsdaisy is in an even position##4
2. the person who's birthday is in october is on the far left or far right##3
3. the person traveling to venice is on the right of the alhambra-smoker##1
4. the person who's birthday is in october is on the left or right of the person who growsdaisy##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2       |
| City         | hannover   | venice |
| Cigar           | alhambra | bluemaster    |
| Birthday   | october      | august         |
| Flower         | tulip   | daisy |

